Package com.genesyslab.platform.webmedia.protocol.espemail.runtime

Class EspEmailBinding

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.genesyslab.platform.webmedia.protocol.espemail.runtime.EspEmailBinding
  • public final class EspEmailBinding
extends java.lang.Object
    Class contains functionality for marshaling/unmarshaling data between key value collection and appropriate object of predefined class. Predefined classes are generating according to protocol description.
